title: ArtyTorrent Pack 68-Big Beat Breaks 130-139bpm-WAV samples
description:
ArtyTorrent Pack 68-Big Beat Breaks 130-139bpm-WAV samples
----------------------------------------------------------

A variety of live and digital breakbeats. Most of these samples are quite highly compressed, so they are ideal for Big Beat or Industrial productions, but they can also be used for other genres
with a tempo range from 130-139 bpm.

Torrent contains 6 RAR files with 80 loops
------------------------------------------
Breakbeat kit 135 (9 loops)
ChFire Breaks 130-135 (14 loops)
DDT Breakz 130-139 (12 loops)
SF Big Beat 130 (25 loops)
Shadow Kit 138 (7 loops)
Street Beats 130 (13 loops)

Samples are from a variety of sources including Sony/Sonic Foundry, Loopology/Syntrillium, and  have all been normalized and acidized as 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz. Approx tempo is included in each filename.

--
Arty - "Break time"
18th February 2008.
